episodes.title: The missing 6, cult ties and a new lead
episodes.description:
The missing six include 28-year-old Ma’Kayla Wickerson with her daughter, now 5-year-old Malaiyah Wickerson. Then, there’s 27-year-old Mikayla Thompson and 30-year-old Gerrielle German, with her 5-year-old daughter Ashton Mitchell.

They all vanished along with 32-year-old Naaman Williams.

All of them are believed to be connected to an online cult called the “University of Cosmic Intelligence.”

episodes.title: Still no trace of vanished members of online cult
episodes.description:
Police say the individuals were part of an online cult that reportedly has 10,000 followers. All six disappeared without a trace, with some believing they may be in Mexico. FOX 2’s Max Diekneite reports.
